00:00:31.820 --> 00:00:35.180
=Twin Fates=

00:00:35.180 --> 00:00:38.140
=Episode 6=
(Kiss Me. There's No Time)

00:00:42.360 --> 00:00:43.160
This is bad.

00:00:44.280 --> 00:00:45.200
There's no time.

00:00:48.120 --> 00:00:49.280
(Twin-soul Contract.)

00:00:49.880 --> 00:00:51.480
(Saving her is saving myself.)

00:01:47.520 --> 00:01:48.320
(Chi Yu,)

00:01:49.480 --> 00:01:51.920
(the phoenix's three golden feathers)

00:01:52.320 --> 00:01:53.600
(are a divine gift.)

00:01:54.000 --> 00:01:56.120
(Pulling out the golden feather
can kill you.)

00:01:56.120 --> 00:01:57.120
(The harm is irreversible.)

00:01:58.040 --> 00:01:59.080
(How many more times)

00:01:59.080 --> 00:02:00.440
(can you save this weak human?)

00:02:01.100 --> 00:02:02.480
(Once all the golden feathers
are used up,)

00:02:02.480 --> 00:02:03.680
(we'll both lose our divine body.)

00:02:04.400 --> 00:02:06.400
(If you don't cherish this body,)

00:02:07.160 --> 00:02:09.240
(I'll do it.)

00:02:11.040 --> 00:02:11.840
Get out!

00:02:17.040 --> 00:02:17.840
(An Sha!)

00:02:18.320 --> 00:02:19.520
(If you hurt her,)

00:02:19.760 --> 00:02:21.280
(I'll destroy this body.)

00:03:10.440 --> 00:03:11.480
She's awake?

00:03:12.600 --> 00:03:14.880
How could she still be alive after being struck
by the poisoned needle?

00:03:16.000 --> 00:03:16.840
I believe

00:03:17.320 --> 00:03:19.440
she was saved by the guard by her side.

00:03:19.880 --> 00:03:21.440
This man is indeed no ordinary person.

00:03:21.800 --> 00:03:24.200
We must find a way
to get rid of him first.

00:03:25.360 --> 00:03:26.160
By the way,

00:03:26.760 --> 00:03:27.880
His Majesty and Lord Yi

00:03:27.880 --> 00:03:29.720
heard Princess Qingci had fallen sick

00:03:29.720 --> 00:03:31.320
and had already rushed back.

00:03:34.040 --> 00:03:36.920
They truly care about her.

00:03:46.520 --> 00:03:47.680
(Where is Chi Yu?)

00:03:47.680 --> 00:03:49.000
(Did something happen?)

00:03:49.320 --> 00:03:50.520
(Let me try a sneeze.)

00:03:57.800 --> 00:03:59.000
Are you all right, Chi Yu?

00:04:03.240 --> 00:04:04.440
What's wrong, Chi Yu?

00:04:05.280 --> 00:04:06.080
What are you doing?

00:04:22.720 --> 00:04:23.560
What's wrong with you?

00:04:41.440 --> 00:04:42.240
Kiss me.

00:04:43.000 --> 00:04:43.800
Are you insane?

00:04:44.200 --> 00:04:45.600
I can't control him.

00:04:47.120 --> 00:04:47.920
Kiss me.

00:04:48.960 --> 00:04:50.320
(Could it be that his body)

00:04:50.320 --> 00:04:51.680
(have two souls?)

00:05:12.200 --> 00:05:14.520
His Majesty, Lord Yi,

00:05:14.520 --> 00:05:16.920
and Lord Yi's heiress have arrived.

00:05:22.560 --> 00:05:24.640
That guard is in her room.

00:05:46.160 --> 00:05:47.200
Ci,

00:05:47.200 --> 00:05:48.760
His Majesty heard you fell ill,

00:05:48.800 --> 00:05:49.920
so he has come to see you.

00:05:58.520 --> 00:05:59.160
Qingci,

00:05:59.280 --> 00:06:00.280
I'm here to see you.

00:06:01.080 --> 00:06:02.120
(Now.)

00:06:02.520 --> 00:06:03.760
There's an assassin in her room.

00:06:03.760 --> 00:06:05.240
Quick. Protect His Majesty.

00:06:10.680 --> 00:06:11.600
Go.

00:06:13.040 --> 00:06:13.960
Don't be afraid, Qingci.

00:06:14.160 --> 00:06:15.960
Someone saw an assassin in your room.

00:06:16.040 --> 00:06:17.480
For the sake of His Majesty

00:06:17.520 --> 00:06:18.800
and your safety.

00:06:18.840 --> 00:06:20.080
We must search immediately.

00:06:23.840 --> 00:06:24.800
What assassin?

00:06:25.040 --> 00:06:27.040
Are you trying to embarrass me
without proof?

00:06:43.600 --> 00:06:45.440
My servant saw it.

00:06:46.200 --> 00:06:48.440
Are you being coerced?

00:06:48.640 --> 00:06:50.800
Or is the assassin

00:06:52.320 --> 00:06:54.240
actually your servant?

00:07:05.400 --> 00:07:06.720
Since I returned,

00:07:06.880 --> 00:07:09.000
I don't know how I offended you.

00:07:09.320 --> 00:07:11.520
You keep humiliating
and making things hard for me.

00:07:12.240 --> 00:07:13.640
First you questioned my identity

00:07:13.840 --> 00:07:15.160
and forced me to undress
before everyone.

00:07:15.840 --> 00:07:17.480
Now you barged in with a group of people

00:07:17.680 --> 00:07:19.040
while I was taking a medicinal bath.

00:07:19.160 --> 00:07:21.200
You're trying to ruin my reputation.

00:07:34.440 --> 00:07:35.640
(Playing the victim)

00:07:35.640 --> 00:07:37.080
(won't work on me.)

00:07:38.320 --> 00:07:40.040
What has happened, Qingci?

00:07:45.840 --> 00:07:47.600
Isn't making me look bad enough for you?

00:07:48.200 --> 00:07:49.000
That's enough!

00:07:52.000 --> 00:07:52.480
Father,

00:07:52.600 --> 00:07:54.640
an assassination attempt
in a lord's residence is a grave crime.

00:07:55.000 --> 00:07:57.480
The assassin may be hiding in this tub.

00:08:04.640 --> 00:08:05.800
If you want to check,

00:08:05.960 --> 00:08:07.120
I'll let you.

00:08:16.720 --> 00:08:17.520
Everyone leave.

00:08:22.880 --> 00:08:24.040
I came here

00:08:24.600 --> 00:08:26.120
to visit Qingci.

00:08:26.240 --> 00:08:27.840
I didn't expect the heiress

00:08:28.160 --> 00:08:30.080
to stage such an act.

00:08:30.760 --> 00:08:32.560
How very thoughtful.

00:08:34.520 --> 00:08:36.320
Your Majesty, please believe me.

00:08:36.320 --> 00:08:37.120
Shut up.

00:08:38.280 --> 00:08:40.040
Isn't this causing enough of a scene?

00:08:41.960 --> 00:08:43.640
Father.

00:08:48.880 --> 00:08:50.320
(He must be here.)

00:08:50.680 --> 00:08:52.520
(If I can find him,)

00:08:52.680 --> 00:08:54.480
(I can prove I'm right.)

00:09:10.440 --> 00:09:11.320
Your Majesty.

00:09:11.520 --> 00:09:12.160
Guards.

00:09:12.400 --> 00:09:13.400
Lock her up

00:09:13.600 --> 00:09:14.520
to reflect on her actions.

00:09:14.600 --> 00:09:15.720
Father!

00:09:16.120 --> 00:09:17.640
Father, believe me.

00:09:17.640 --> 00:09:20.040
Your Majesty, believe me.

00:09:20.160 --> 00:09:21.160
Father!

00:09:40.400 --> 00:09:41.280
Chi Yu.

00:09:42.480 --> 00:09:43.520
Wake up, Chi Yu.

00:09:45.240 --> 00:09:46.120
Wake up.

00:09:49.600 --> 00:09:51.000
I'm losing control of him.

00:09:52.280 --> 00:09:53.080
Kiss me.

00:09:55.240 --> 00:09:56.200
Could it be

00:09:56.520 --> 00:09:57.560
that

00:09:57.560 --> 00:09:59.360
the kiss time isn't long enough?

00:10:34.240 --> 00:10:35.480
(Why hasn't he woken up yet?)

00:10:40.820 --> 00:10:46.060
♪Bit by bit,
reality shatters my only hope♪

00:10:46.860 --> 00:10:52.380
♪Layer by layer, cold blades roll up
the light I once glimpsed in secret♪

00:10:52.380 --> 00:10:55.260
♪Letters have long since yellowed♪

00:10:55.260 --> 00:10:59.020
♪Leaving only two lonely lines♪

00:10:59.780 --> 00:11:04.380
♪Even the old yard is covered
with frost♪

00:11:04.380 --> 00:11:09.700
♪Pair after pair,
swallows draw my envious gaze♪

00:11:10.100 --> 00:11:15.740
♪Scene after scene,
in dreams I cannot reach♪

00:11:15.740 --> 00:11:18.740
♪While you rest beneath the earth♪

00:11:18.740 --> 00:11:20.240
♪My love lingers in this frosty world♪

00:11:20.240 --> 00:11:20.680
I saw

00:11:21.480 --> 00:11:22.720
you fainted just now,

00:11:22.720 --> 00:11:23.720
so I...

00:11:26.360 --> 00:11:28.000
Are you all right?

00:11:30.920 --> 00:11:31.800
I'm fine.

00:11:34.560 --> 00:11:36.000
Your wound.

00:11:36.880 --> 00:11:38.520
Did you get hurt trying to save me?

00:11:40.600 --> 00:11:41.920
It's not what you think.

00:12:18.800 --> 00:12:19.400
Father...

00:12:30.240 --> 00:12:31.400
Did Father send you?

00:12:32.760 --> 00:12:33.640
Try this.

00:12:34.960 --> 00:12:36.320
Flower cake from Zhiwei Pavilion.

00:12:36.800 --> 00:12:37.920
Your favorite.

00:12:47.200 --> 00:12:48.240
You took everything from me.

00:12:48.240 --> 00:12:49.720
Are you proud of that?

00:12:50.800 --> 00:12:52.680
You'll meet a grimmer end than I did.

00:12:52.680 --> 00:12:54.440
You're not Ji Qingci at all!

00:12:56.040 --> 00:12:58.760
It's no different
from a street stall.

00:13:09.960 --> 00:13:11.800
Looks like you still don't understand.

00:13:12.400 --> 00:13:13.880
Whether I'm Ji Qingci or not

00:13:13.880 --> 00:13:15.240
is not the point.

00:13:15.680 --> 00:13:16.840
Because no matter what you do,

00:13:16.840 --> 00:13:18.560
you can never change the fact

00:13:19.120 --> 00:13:20.840
that you'll always

00:13:20.840 --> 00:13:23.320
be only an illegitimate daughter.

00:13:25.400 --> 00:13:26.320
Just why?

00:13:27.240 --> 00:13:29.240
We're both Father's daughters.

00:13:29.760 --> 00:13:32.480
But why does Father only see Ji Qingci?

00:13:32.640 --> 00:13:33.440
Why can Ji Qingci

00:13:33.440 --> 00:13:35.760
easily take everything
that belongs to me?

00:13:36.240 --> 00:13:37.720
Why didn't she just die?

00:13:41.680 --> 00:13:42.800
I'll give you a choice.

00:13:43.280 --> 00:13:45.120
Tell me
where Lord Yi's secret account is,

00:13:45.480 --> 00:13:46.920
and I'll get you out of here.

00:13:48.240 --> 00:13:50.840
How did you know
about the secret account?

00:13:51.200 --> 00:13:52.880
Who are you, really?

00:13:53.440 --> 00:13:55.040
(I knew something was wrong
with Lord Yi.)

00:13:57.600 --> 00:13:58.880
You tricked me.

00:14:00.320 --> 00:14:01.120
You!

00:14:02.560 --> 00:14:03.440
No matter who I really am,

00:14:03.440 --> 00:14:05.040
right now I am Ji Qingci.

00:14:05.320 --> 00:14:07.120
It's thanks to your schemes

00:14:07.160 --> 00:14:08.640
and the way you kept
giving yourself away

00:14:08.640 --> 00:14:11.080
that my identity as the legitimate
daughter was finally confirmed.

00:14:17.720 --> 00:14:19.680
You can never get the secret account.

00:14:25.000 --> 00:14:26.680
Even if you don't tell me where it is,

00:14:26.680 --> 00:14:27.720
it's fine.

00:14:28.480 --> 00:14:30.120
With my current position,

00:14:30.720 --> 00:14:32.800
it's only a matter of time.

00:14:33.880 --> 00:14:34.720
You, on the other hand,

00:14:35.960 --> 00:14:37.880
have already lost.

00:14:46.360 --> 00:14:49.200
Ji Qingci!

00:14:49.440 --> 00:14:52.240
Let me out!

00:15:02.400 --> 00:15:03.640
(Why is my face so red?)

00:15:12.600 --> 00:15:13.800
(What am I even thinking?)

00:15:15.040 --> 00:15:15.840
(Calm down.)

00:15:16.680 --> 00:15:17.600
(Calm down.)

